type.description: The type of the event, always `response.output_text.done`.

sequence_number.description: The sequence number of the event that was emitted.

item_id.description: The ID of the item that was updated.

output_index.description: The index of the output item that was updated.

content_index.description: The index of the content part that was completed.

text.description: The final text that was emitted.

logprobs.description: The token log probabilities that were emitted with the final text, if any.

title: Response output text done event
description: A streaming event that indicated output text was completed.
